snippet.title: Electronauts: People Under the Stairs Feature
snippet.description:
Wishlist ELECTRONAUTS on Steam: bit.ly/ElectronautsSteam
Follow ELECTRONAUTS on Instagram: instagram.com/electronautsvr

ELECTRONAUTS featured artists People Under the Stairs share their thoughts on how the new VR music creation experience has the potential to revolutionize beatmaking.

Survios's VR music creation experience ELECTRONAUTS features 40+ songs from 50 top artists including The Chainsmokers, Tiesto, Zhu, Krewella, and more! Immerse yourself in an interactive sonic environment where you build, drop, remix, and jam with your friends and top artists. Create songs, crush sets, and express yourself like never before. ELECTRONAUTS sets the stage for you to DJ, perform, and make music magic in virtual reality.
